nodes.title: FacePos/Pose generator
widgets_values: Idea: i can use a very fast, low quality model to generate the ideal framing/pose/face, use an extractor like this, then feed this into the actual generator (InstantID). That way, i can independently control framing such that it's different each time. Could be cartoon generator even? I could have an LLM write the prompt, or the pose/position, which generates the image that's fed into the extractor
